Basic Installation
-------------------

Create a build directory:
mkdir build

Change directory to build:
cd build

Run cmake in the build directory:
cmake ..

If you want to add debug info to Aki:
cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=debugfull

It defaults to /usr/local if you want to change that run this:
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<directory to install to>

Afterwards run:
make

And to install run:
make install
